        "name": "Falcon Swoop",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "Like the fastest of predatory birds, you soar toward your prey at great speeds. Fly twice. At any point during this movement, you can make a Strike against one enemy within reach or within the first range increment of a ranged weapon. That enemy is off-guard against the Strike if you're attacking them from above.",
        "level": 10,
